name: websharper.fs.fluentui.testgrounds
description: The proxy template is intended for creating a JavaScript-only accompanying library for an existing .NET library. Add code files to the project, and it will produce a `.dll` file that has no .NET content, but contains full WebSharper translation and metadata. It can be referenced next to the original library in another project, so that both server-side and client-side functionality are available.
